OL,5,G1800 Kent: The Garden of England
OL,6,     FWe visit Hever Castle - once home
OL,7,     Fto Anne Boleyn - with its
OL,8,     Fincredible gardens; climb to
OL,9,     FKent's highest village, Ide Hill;
OL,10,     Fand visit Kent's oldest 'modern'
OL,11,     Fvineyard near Biddenden. (Ep4)
OL,12,G1900 Alexander Armstrong Across America
OL,13,     FAlexander explores one of the
OL,14,     Fworld's most powerful, complex
OL,15,     Fcountries, starting in
OL,16,     FPhiladelphia, where he sees
OL,17,     Fcontrasts - from the Declaration
OL,18,     Fof Independence to the opioid
OL,19,     Fcrisis.
